  <description type="morphology">Plants 3–6 dm. Aerial flowering stems fistulose, 1–3 dm, glabrous. Leaves basal; blade 1–2 × 0.3–0.8 dm, tomentose abaxially, tomentose to floccose adaxially, margins undulate-crisped. Inflorescences often cymose, 10–30 × 5–20 cm; branches glabrous. Involucres 1(–2) per cluster, 3–5 mm, glabrous. Flowers 2.5–3 mm; perianth yellow or, infrequently, white, pubescent.</description>
